  <description><![CDATA[<p><span>The Banff Aspen Lodge is a popular hotel situated just three minutes' walk from the shops and restaurants of Banff Downtown. </span></p>
<h2><span>Sleek design</span></h2>
<p><span>The hotel is modern and well designed. The lobby has an open fireplace to warm yourself by and the rooms are spacious with modern amenities.</span></p>
<h2><span>Hot tub hideaway</span></h2>
<p><span>Soak up the Rocky Mountain air in the hotel's </span>courtyard with two hot tub pools, or warm up after a day in the snow at the outdoor fireplace.</p>
<h2>Downtown location</h2>
<p>You are in the heart of <a data-udi="umb://document/3f77e79eea2d4582a9acb3c89406dc88" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3f77e79eea2d4582a9acb3c89406dc88}" title="Banff">Banff</a> at the Banff Aspen Lodge. The great restaurants, bars, shops and cafes that the resort has to offer are just a few minutes walk away.</p>
<p>The ski bus stop is nearby too so you can explore the incredible national park easily and see all that Banff and <a data-udi="umb://document/7cf5e06f2ccd4cf8b8f46d06ca905a75" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7cf5e06f2ccd4cf8b8f46d06ca905a75}" title="Lake Louise">Lake Louise</a> have to offer.</p>]]></description>
